                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1395-18390408 t18390408-1395-punishment-228"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</hi>
               </p>
